Sentencas: Using mixed proton and oxide - ion conductor with BaCe0.9 Y-0.1 O3-alpha as a solid electrolyte, hydrogen - air fuel cell was constructed.
Titulo: Performance of solid oxide fuel cell using BaCe0.9Y0.1O3-α as a solid electrolyte

Sentencas: The performances of the cell were investigated at temperatures between 600 and 1000 degreesC.
Titulo: Performance of solid oxide fuel cell using BaCe0.9Y0.1O3-α as a solid electrolyte

Sentencas: The maximum short - circuit current density and the maximum power output density of this cell at 1000 degreesC were about 980mA .
Titulo: Performance of solid oxide fuel cell using BaCe0.9Y0.1O3-α as a solid electrolyte
Performance of solid oxide fuel cell using BaCe0.9Y0.1O3-α as a solid electrolyte
Performance of solid oxide fuel cell using BaCe0.9Y0.1O3-α as a solid electrolyte

Sentencas: These performances were significantly better than those of other solid oxide fuel cells based on BaCe0.9M0.1O3-alpha (M = Sm, Gd, Yb, Nd, etc.) reported so far.
Titulo: Performance of solid oxide fuel cell using BaCe0.9Y0.1O3-α as a solid electrolyte
